Mother&#39;s Pride World School, Chakarbhata, Bilaspur celebrated The Annual Function 2.0 &quot;Udaan - Prideens&#39; Flight of Success&quot; (2025-2026) on 20.12.2025. Chairman Mr. Sabino D&#39;Souza, Vice-Chairman Mr. Ramkumar Arya, Principal Ms.Vandana D&#39;Souza , Secretary Mr.Sylvester D&#39;Souza, Joint Secretary Mr. Shyamkumar Arya
welcomed Honourable MLA Mr. Dharamlal Kaushik ji as the Chief Guest of the Day. The Guest of Honour of the Day was Ms.Neelam Vijay Verma. Honorable Mr. Kaushik ji appreciated the school’s rapid progress and notable achievements since its establishment. The Honourable MLA also interacted with the students backstage, motivating them to present an energetic and confident performance. He also appreciated the holistic development of the students under the wise guidance of the Chairman, Principal and the entire team members of the School." class="x5yr21d xu96u03 x10l6tqk x13vifvy x87ps6o xh8yej3" crossorigin="anonymous" src="./Instagram2_files/631897681_18039348491766184_7433350831975447670_n.jpg" style="object-fit: cover;"></div><div class="_aagw"></div></div><div class="html-div xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x78zum5 x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw x1uhb9sk x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xdt5ytf xqjyukv x1qjc9v5 x1oa3qoh x1nhvcw1"><div class="xuk3077 x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x1ey2m1c x9f619 x78zum5 xdt5ytf x2lah0s xln7xf2 xk390pu xtijo5x x1o0tod x1nhvcw1 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x47corl x10l6tqk x13vifvy x11njtxf"><div class="html-div xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x78zum5 x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw x1xmf6yo x1xegmmw x1e56ztr x13fj5qh x1n2onr6 x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xdt5ytf xqjyukv x1qjc9v5 x1oa3qoh x1nhvcw1"><svg aria-label="Clip" class="x1lliihq x1n2onr6 x9bdzbf" fill="currentColor" height="20" role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20"><title>Clip</title><path d="M22.942 7.464c-.062-1.36-.306-2.143-.511-2.671a5.366 5.366 0 0 0-1.272-1.952 5.364 5.364 0 0 0-1.951-1.27c-.53-.207-1.312-.45-2.673-.513-1.2-.054-1.557-.066-4.535-.066s-3.336.012-4.536.066c-1.36.062-2.143.306-2.672.511-.769.3-1.371.692-1.951 1.272s-.973 1.182-1.27 1.951c-.207.53-.45 1.312-.513 2.673C1.004 8.665.992 9.022.992 12s.012 3.336.066 4.536c.062 1.36.306 2.143.