Glimpses of *Grandparents* *Day* celebration in school.

 Our *Grandparents* are our historians, our secret-keepers, our biggest cheerleaders, and the ones whose love feels like a warm hug.

They give the best advice, tell the best stories, and have a magical way of making everything better. Their wisdom and unconditional love are gifts that shape who we are.

To all the grandparents: thank you for your endless love, your priceless stories, and for making our lives so much richer. We wouldn&#39;t be who we are without you.

