Our  school was overflowing with love and joy during our *Parenting Activity* session of *Nursery Class* . It was truly heartwarming to watch our parents and children collaborate, create, and share so many smiles.

These activities are so much more than just crafts and games; they are the building blocks of confidence, trust, and a lifelong love for learning. Thank you for partnering with us and for being such engaged and wonderful participants in your child&#39;s education.

