Today, our school was filled with divine energy as we celebrated **Janmashtami**—the birth of Lord Krishna! 🌺🎶 From beautiful decorations to soulful bhajans and colorful dance performances , the day was truly magical. 

Our little **Kanhas** and **Gopis** stole the show with their adorable attire and devotion! 

May Lord Krishna bless us all with love, wisdom, and endless joy! ✨🪔 

